sentences: Aneta Sablik (born 12 January 1989) is a Polish singer-songwriter.
She was announced the winner of season 11 on 3 May 2014, winning €500,000, a car, and a record label contract.
Sablik signed a contract with Polydor Records (owned by Universal Music Group) to release her debut album, titled The One in late 2014.
She digitally launched her debut single "The One" on the same day of winning season 11, which topped music charts in Germany, Austria, Switzerland, and Luxembourg.
